{"text_id":172634,"tokens":["The"," psychological"," impact"," of"," perpet","rating"," mass"," violence"," on"," the"," rank","-","and","-","file"," SS"," members"," has"," been"," extensively"," studied"," by"," historians",","," psychologists",","," and"," sociologists","."," While"," Him","mler","'","s"," diary"," entry"," suggests"," that"," the"," men"," of"," the"," SS"," Einsatz","gruppen"," were"," either"," '","neuro","tics"," or"," br","utes","',"," research"," suggests"," a"," more"," complex"," and"," nuanced"," understanding"," of"," their"," psychological"," profiles",".","\n\n","Studies"," have"," shown"," that"," the"," majority"," of"," SS"," members"," did"," not"," exhibit"," sad","istic"," or"," brutal"," personalities"," before"," joining"," the"," organization","."," Instead",","," they"," were"," often"," ordinary"," individuals"," who"," were"," social","ized"," into"," a"," culture"," of"," violence"," and"," obedience"," through"," the"," SS","'","s"," rigorous"," training"," and"," indoctr","ination"," programs","."," This"," process"," involved"," a"," gradual"," des","ensi","tization"," to"," violence",","," de","human","ization"," of"," the"," victims",","," and"," a"," strong"," emphasis"," on"," loyalty"," and"," camaraderie"," among"," the"," group",".","\n\n","After"," the"," war",","," many"," SS"," members"," were"," able"," to"," re","integrate"," into"," society"," without"," displaying"," overt"," signs"," of"," psychological"," distress","."," However",","," research"," has"," revealed"," that"," a"," significant"," proportion"," of"," them"," suffered"," from"," long","-","term"," psychological"," trauma",","," including"," anxiety",","," depression",","," and"," nightmares","."," Studies"," have"," also"," shown"," that"," many"," SS"," members"," experienced"," feelings"," of"," guilt",","," shame",","," and"," remorse",","," which"," were"," often"," suppressed"," or"," denied"," due"," to"," the"," social"," stigma"," as